Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------PREV-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她直到最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉欧在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界也变得绚丽多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星移民计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因其失败被遗留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称独立国家维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向地球联邦政府宣战
