Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么会有高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音…难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作为地球圈的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须亲眼见证维甘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的BOSS登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您快走 这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吸引他的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在离开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是汇合坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里的目的就是救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 快走 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走啊 我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 锥炮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台高达雷吉鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对AGE-3进行分析研究
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并加入EXA-DB技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造而成的新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在它面前没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有东西要让你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在火星圈 遇到许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了维甘不全是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球圈有很多人在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我不能回到你那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就和我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打败我你才能回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我…和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么天真无法幸存！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见证了火星圈的悲惨现实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该了解我们为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要夺回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 质问那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是否有活着的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解我一片苦心！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别听他的胡言乱语 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的存在太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是现在就干掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有那种必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达和吉欧 我都要活捉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖投降对你有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一个人在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续射击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但凡包围圈这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微在哪里戳它一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会轻易垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我使劲打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去歼灭碍事的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人的命令必须遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧 才没那种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再做这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉地球上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星圈的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非想让维甘的人民移居地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有打算歼灭地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里告诉你 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是伊甸计划的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸…计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从世界上出现人类的那一刻起就有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有限的资源和有限的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为争夺这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类反复上演着鲜血书写的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去人类终有一天会自取灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我精心准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为创造一个绝对不存在争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由贤明的人类所组成的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在极限环境下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同人的大脑和身体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到DNA序列支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会采取不同的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在调查的基础上鉴别出更优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以袭击诺拉和天使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是为营造出极限环境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在维甘的卫星中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾伪装成事故 制造过相同的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为选出能担负起人类新时代重任的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更优秀的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为创造没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为创造安宁与和平的理想乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不分维甘与联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有优秀种群可以在那里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是那个乐园的建立者！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 这么纤细的缆索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妄想困住扎姆多拉格！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的只是让你停下一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个挺有意思的对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为海盗来说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙硬得就像块臭石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大副 这样下去危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 让他们给我顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有几分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 都怪那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它 把我们的计划全打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这么残忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为救人类逃脱灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过鉴别优秀的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此使战乱在人类的历史中消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那些没有被选中的人怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在实现伟大理想的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的人们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们那么信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和露乌都那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也失去了罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我自己所剩的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 决不能沉浸于一时的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住在一个没有争斗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们会心的微笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是… 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我毕生追求的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉德克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出G拦截机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G拦截机？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要亲手打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通往新世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都能活得有尊严！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈也没去过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果转世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想生在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要你们做我的爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们一起在地球上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是他的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是他转世投胎重新回到我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不明白我的苦衷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不会是唯一的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用发动战争也有其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是你的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史证明了人类无法斩断暴力的链锁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达跟不上我的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗 拉德克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大副 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 接通信号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即停止战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 立即停止战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不满足我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让这些小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砸向你们的殖民地 第二月球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 敌众我寡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧我带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,180度调头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 把它们给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹带着干扰物的虚拟气球？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太看不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追！不能让他们活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在追击也为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军返航
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有听见我的命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说当时就应该干掉高达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该 维甘这些傻瓜吃瘪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他们也该瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么哭丧着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大副
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备酒宴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一群朝不保夕的亡命之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝酒庆祝才是最合适的悼念方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为选出能担负起人类新时代重任的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更优秀的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为创造没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为创造安宁与和平的理想乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我毕生追求的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该…怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎加入我军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇敢的维甘战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你们所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人已经进犯第二月球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗必将十分惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待你们的勇气！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
